Omnia, Yara Are Cleared in Fertilizer Collusion Case, Business Day Reports

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-03-16T05:01:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-16/omnia-yara-are-cleared-in-fertilizer-collusion-case-business-day-reports.html
  Omnia Holdings Ltd. (OMN)  and the South
African unit of  Yara International ASA (YAR)  have been cleared by the
Competition Appeals Court of collusion charges in the fertilizer
market, Business Day reported, citing Competition Commission
advocacy and stakeholder manager Oupa Bodibe.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  